title: Human Powered Health close in on Women’s WorldTour survival as points fight nears its end
content:
Chances to score points are dwindling as October approaches and, after looking like it would be demoted, Human Powered Health is on course to keep WorldTout license.

Read the full article at Human Powered Health close in on Women’s WorldTour survival as points fight nears its end on Velo.
author: sadhbhoshea
